cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with action detection and recognition tasks in computer vision, which is a subfield of computer science that falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new attention filtering method and a generalized binary loss function, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses datasets and evaluates its performance, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper mentions applications in robotics (cs.RO).
